videos.description: Joel Embiid lands hard while driving on Robin Lopez and gets up holding his back.

videos.headline: Embiid slow to get up after Lopez blocks him

videos.description: Bradley Beal appears to injure his knee during a fast-break play and immediately limps off to the Wizards' bench.

videos.headline: Beal limps off the court with his shoe in hand

videos.description: Tyrese Maxey barely beats the shot clock with a 3-pointer on Russell Westbrook.

videos.headline: Maxey drains a 3-pointer over Westbrook

videos.description: Capital One Arena erupts in cheers after Russell Westbrook skies for a thunderous putback.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Westbrook's putback dunk gets the Wizards' arena fired up) 2021/5/31 ESHEET

videos.headline: Westbrook's putback dunk gets the Wizards' arena fired up

videos.description: Rui Hachimura cleans up Bradley Beal's miss with massive putback slam and receives a technical foul for taunting.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Hachimura gets T'd up for taunting after monstrous dunk) 2021/5/31 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hachimura gets T'd up for taunting after monstrous dunk

videos.description: A fan's attempt to run on the court midgame gets thwarted by a security guard.

videos.headline: Fan on court tackled by security during Sixers-Wizards Game 4

videos.description: Daniel Gafford flies through the lane to clean up Bradley Beal's miss with a booming putback dunk.

videos.headline: Gafford wrecks the rim on roaring putback

videos.headline: Hachimura flushes massive dunk

videos.description: Bradley Beal navigates through traffic and kicks to Rui Hachimura for a 3-pointer to extend the Wizards' lead.

videos.headline: Hachimura fired up after nailing clutch 3-pointer
